Installing
==========

Installing SMFL (Windows)
-------------------------

Install SMFL from http://www.sfml-dev.org/

Add an Environment Variable named SFMLDIR, set it to the SFML folder.


Installing SMFL and OpenGL (Ubuntu)
-----------------------------------


Run
	sudo apt-get install libglew1.5-dev libjpeg8-dev libopenal-dev libsndfile1-dev libbullet-dev libv8-dev cmake
	git clone https://github.com/LaurentGomila/SFML.git
	cd SFML && cmake . && make install
	cd ../Magnetite && cmake .
	
	#Add these to /etc/apt/sources.list
	#deb http://ppa.launchpad.net/christoph-egger/ubuntu hardy main
	#deb-src http://ppa.launchpad.net/christoph-egger/ubuntu hardy main
	#mesa-common-dev libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev
	#libsfml-dev libcsfml-dev

Building
========
Run cmake
Run make
